The '''Elk River Wind Project''' is a 150 megawatt [[wind farm]] near [[Beaumont, Kansas|Beaumont]] in [[Butler County, Kansas]]. The Elk River wind plant's subsidiary is owned by a parent company. The plant has been operating since 2005.<ref>[http://www.kansasenergy.org/wind_projects.htm#elk Kansas Wind Projects - Elk River Wind Project]</ref>

Empire District Electric selected [[Elk River (Kansas)|Elk River]], and signed a twenty-year agreement with [[Iberdrola|PPM Energy]] to purchase wind energy from the farm.<ref>[http://www.ppmenergy.com/cs_elkriver.html/ Elk River Wind Project]</ref>

